      "offset": 0,
      "text": "The great sages, approaching Manu who was seated with a concentrated mind, duly honored him according to custom and spoke these words: // Mn_1.1 //"
    },
    {
      "id": "p-b51d68",
      "offset": 149,
      "text": "\"O divine Lord, it is right for you to declare to us, precisely and in order, the sacred laws for all the four *varnas* (social orders) and for those born between them. // Mn_1.2 //"
    },
    {
      "id": "p-f3134c",
      "offset": 332,
      "text": "For you alone, O Lord, know the true meaning of the purpose and reality of this entire ordinance of the Self-existent One, which is inconceivable and immeasurable.\" // Mn_1.3 //"
    }
  ]
}

