    {
      "id": "p-979379",
      "offset": 128,
      "text": "1. The steadfast one, seeking battle on the field of austerities and vows, warring against the six heroic enemies within,\nHis battle-array is the quality of truth in meditation; his chariot, the practice of compassion and more.\nThe sacred hand-gestures are his banner, the lion's roar his chanted spell, the supreme bow his inconceivable contemplation;\nThe highest arrow is enlightenment-wisdom, annihilating the foe, bearing the fruit of *dharma*-*śūnyatā*."
    }
  ]
}

