      "id": "p-c757ea",
      "offset": 35392,
      "text": "10. \"But as for his arrival in Yama's realm,\nin seven nights he is expected to come.\nThat is the reason the cauldron is being washed,\nas the place of his torment when he arrives.\""
    },
    {
      "id": "p-f0a566",
      "offset": 35573,
      "text": "11. \"Oh, how fruitful is the Lord God's instruction!\nMy heart feels as if it has been sliced, hearing this.\nI long to become a human in the future;\nI see the pity of being a man is a difficult thing.\""
    },
    {
      "id": "p-2093a7",
      "offset": 35775,
      "text": "12. \"Again I ask of the Lord Yama:\nwho is the name of that sinner?\nCome, tell me, sir.\nIt seems you know his name.\""
    },
